  <h2 class="txt">
	BCA Math Competition</h2>
  <h3 class="txt">President's Address:</h3>
<p>Welcome to the Fourth Annual BCA Math Competition for 4th through 8th grade students!<br>
This competition brings  the best and brightest elementary and middle school students from Bergen County and the surrounding area to the Bergen County Academies to meet and compete with fellow students. </p>
